       <item>
          <title>vrijdag 18 januari 2019 - Just Kidding Comedy Leiden</title>
          <description><![CDATA[
          Out with the Old and in with the Jokes! It's the 2019 Premiere of Just Kidding Comedy Leiden, Friday January 18th @ 8:00pm at the Muziekhuis in Leiden!<br><br>This month we welcome Liam Withnail (UK), German wonder Michael Jager, a special guest and your MC Carly Baker (USA). <br><br>**This show is entirely in ENGLISH**<br><br>LIAM WITHNAIL- Hailing from Dagenham, England with an Irish mom...Liam prefers to hide in Scotland most of his days along side his Aussie wife to feel like he truly belongs. <br>NOMINATED Best Show - 2018 Edinburgh Festival (Amused Moose), WINNER 2018 Scottish Comedy Award, FINALIST Scottish &amp; English Comedian of the Year<br>★★★★★ - Ed Fest Mag<br>★★★★ - One4Review<br><br>MICHAEL JAGER- One of the broadest shouldered, funniest Germans you will ever meet on the comedy circuit. A regular all over Europe most recently playing at the Luxembourg International Comedy Festival and the host of It's Complicated: True Dating Stories monthly ..don't miss him!<br><br>And resident MC Carly Baker (USA) will hold our show together!<br><br>Doors open @ 7:15pm, showtime is 8:00 sharp.<br><br>Online price : 12Euro <br>Online Student price: 9.99Euro<br>Door ticket price: 15 Euro (CASH only)<br>Student price: 12Euro (CASH only)<br><br>BUY ONLINE TICKETS to avoid disappointment.Tickets are more expensive at the door. STUDENT DISCOUNT TICKETS ALSO AVAILABLE online.<br><br>BUY TICKETS HERE:<br>https://shop.ikbenaanwezig.nl/tickets/event/just-kidding-comedy-leiden-jan18th-2<br><br>As we continue into 2019 we are asking all our guests to purchase your ticket online. Keeps it quick and easy at the door! See the link ;)<br>If for some reason this is not possible, please get in touch about reservations via:<br>woodeneye.nl@gmail.com<br><br>Friday, January 18th, 2019<br>8:00pm Show / 7:15 pm Doors<br>Middelstegracht 123, Leiden 2312TV Leiden<br><br>See you all there!!!!<br>Carly and the JKC Crew xx  <br>
          ]]></description>
